# ui file root rules
- @package.json
- The project is a chrome extension
- only use pnpm to install dependencies and devDependencies

# a word prefix with ':' is a command:
:cc - save the size and position of style, only remove color style
:cs - save the color and position of style, only remove size style
:fu - up one level of front size
:fd - down one level of front size
